{"tid":1962614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院: 回應「中共」合作要求","createTime":"2020-04-07T14:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T06:47:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1221,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"0d972f942e511aeeb2206b2521438337eea90817","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"美國國務院發言人Morgan Ortagus:<br />\n<br />\n中共駐美國大使崔天凱呼籲疫情下美中合作, 美國無任歡迎.<br />\n<br />\n中共如想跟美國合作, 請公開<strong>所有</strong>病毒數據, 容許海外專家調查病毒起因, 並向中國人給予言論自由.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1247527621509799938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1247527621509799938&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a6cc5e87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1247527621509799938&h=3433ec3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1247527621509799938</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/wJcRiKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJcRiKX.jpg&h=5b1eeedb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cbe343abed8eb88c610d5422cfc73889ab33fdf","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":122,"dislike":0,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:46:31.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e55258728110829eb225132e086d4418b9aac81","tid":1962614,"uid":301479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af042176ad44e04734fc7f13a0459cbf61a3ca0d","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f338d6c7e9d4f5834d63167d65d603adb3de572","tid":1962614,"uid":244759,"like":283,"dislike":0,"score":283,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"中國有言論自由呀，一生人有一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caed328561036ce91ae41a453d692f5a9b141c3","tid":1962614,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"嘥氣"},{"pid":"4cf7416918e05bd4eca5ee9e8966a3f1b9029540","tid":1962614,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2692af9766c57888a2c41c4f25bd29ce0a1e9e6e","tid":1962614,"uid":326826,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"針對住對手嘅弱點黎發功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d275845c9efd63f8a6c7674215343f48acae46fa","tid":1962614,"uid":202577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"哈 中共都打兩手牌？"},{"pid":"6ee89e2a276325c1b4c974d06721b85371186978","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaf1cff888cebd140fce28de96b90b22d9fdfc2","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161183a07bc8351736401ac12dbb336cdfc6fbe8","tid":1962614,"uid":223741,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"今日選管會選舉活動指引公眾咨詢最後一日(7/4/2020)截止啦<br />\n大家快啲send email反對<br />\n記得自己改少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\neacenq@eac.hk<br />\n<br />\n<ins>反對選管會提出的選舉活動指引</ins><br />\n<br />\n致選舉委員會：<br />\n<br />\n我就選管會就新一屆2020年立法會換屆選舉的選舉活動指引提出反對，反對限制觀看點票人數，以及年滿70歲可優先投票。<br />\n<br />\n首先，根據過往選舉經驗而言，大部份長者選民一般選擇在早上投票。假若長者選民擁有優先投票權，其他需要在早上投票後上班的市民便會增加其時間成本，造成不公平。然而，選舉管理委員會(選管會)應當呼籲長者選民可於其他時段進行投票，避免在票站開站或關閉前的高峰時段前往投票。<br />\n<br />\n再者，即使在過去選舉當中出現長龍，投票過程都十分順利，並無出現大量長者投訴或出現身體不適，可見他們為了投下神聖一票也不會拒絕排隊。若然要解決排長龍這個問題，本人建議可以加開票站疏導，而非使用優先投票這種治標不治本的方法。即使長者能優先投票，人龍依舊存在，並會分開了兩條人龍，更容易造成混亂。<br />\n<br />\n本人建議選管會可以根據2019年區議會選舉時的平等原則作出靈活安排，在排隊人數眾多的時候向未能長時間站立的選民坐下等候，並記下他們的輪候位置，以便在輪到他們的輪候位置時安排他們到發票櫃枱領取選票。<br />\n<br />\n抗議現行法例阻礙18歲人士做選民<br />\n<br />\n本人亦不滿現時法例阻撓部份在選舉日已年滿18歲的人登記成為選民。現時在非區議會選舉年，一名永久性居民要在申請登記為選民後的首個七月二十五日(若為區議會選舉年則為九月二十五日)年滿18歲才成為合資格選民。換言之如果他在2020年7月26日才滿18歲，將無法在2020年度做選民。<br />\n<br />\n反觀外國的做法及法例就不同。加拿大和澳門的做法類似，未滿18歲的人可以事先登記，一到18歲，他們的選民身份就會轉為正式登記，並可以行使選民的權利。<br />\n<br />\n香港的做法是純粹因行政方便而無理剝奪他人選民資格，恐遭司法覆核，選管會應立即修正！<br />\n<br />\n另外本人反對限制觀看點票人數。這會令一些打算觀看點票，以監察選舉結果公平公正的人士無法進入點票站。<br />\n<br />\n本人希望選管會能夠三思而行，盡力在選舉工作上做到公平公正，避免畫蛇添足，招人懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民"},{"pid":"16b11819cdd5bf381e2ddee65fc41efd66f0c595","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791f6994ce6fe4f54820fa880b26a024c2453787","tid":1962614,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdc491b661df874d9a666287a0247de5285de26","tid":1962614,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbe343abed8eb88c610d5422cfc73889ab33fdf","tid":1962614,"uid":134071,"like":122,"dislike":0,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T